data.description:
You will love this 2 bedroom home with natural wood work, formal dining room, stainless steel appliances, updated bath with jetted tub!  Central air.  

Back yard completely privacy fenced in with one stall garage with opener.

Just $895 with $895 deposit.

Pets may be negotiable. Contact us to schedule a showing.
